  "title": "Video by ericnyker",
  "description": "📍Pazonia Italian Street Food @ Amoy\n49 Amoy St, Singapore 069875\n\nGuys @pazonia.sg made me feel that I’ve overpaid for western sandwiches the entire time , not to mention subway…\n\nI could literally eat the Panuozzo Carne everyday lol. Get the burrata to indulge a bit it’s seriously so perfect with the Parma ham. \n\n@pazonia.sg also has a promo going on - for week night dinners- you get the 2nd pizza for 50% off ! It’s from March 3 - 14 :)",
